{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/浏览器事件机制/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"撸猫程序员"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9bc8460f-81de-51cd-b50e-28ef70a4a898","excerpt":"学习 JavaScript 都知道，浏览器的事件触发分为三个阶段。 从最外层容器（通常是 window）向事件触发区域传播。— 捕获阶段（如果注册了捕获事件，将在这个阶段触发） 传播到事件触发区域 — 目标阶段 （触发注册事件） 从触发区域向 window…","html":"<p>学习 JavaScript 都知道，浏览器的事件触发分为三个阶段。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>从最外层容器（通常是 window）向事件触发区域传播。— 捕获阶段（如果注册了捕获事件，将在这个阶段触发）</li>\n<li>传播到事件触发区域 — 目标阶段 （触发注册事件）</li>\n<li>从触发区域向 window 传播 — 冒泡阶段 （如果注册了冒泡事件，将在这个阶段触发）</li>\n</ol>\n<p>一图胜千言：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ow67vzejn.bkt.clouddn.com/20180830112825.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>事件注册</strong></p>\n<p>事件注册分为 3 种（其实是四种），如果包括下面这种最最古老的写法：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>handleClick()<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>srcipt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  function handleClick(){ }\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>srcipt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>不过这种和下面第一种类似（都是上古时期的写法），就归为一种吧。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>传统的事件注册,在元素上使用事件属性。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myDiv\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclick</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>优点：兼容所有浏览器</p>\n<p>缺点：只能注册一个事件处理器（类似于给 onclick 重新赋值），只支持事件冒泡</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>W3C 标准事件注册<code class=\"language-text\">EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></p>\n<p>参数：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>type 事件名（不带 on 的）</li>\n<li>listener （文档说实现了 <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventListener\"><code class=\"language-text\">EventListener</code></a> 接口的对象，或者是一个函数，其实具体使用上就是一个函数）</li>\n<li>[options] 一个对象，指定 listener 的一些行为</li>\n<li>[useCapture] 布尔值，默认 false，为 true 时表面事件在捕获阶段触发，否则在冒泡阶段触发</li>\n</ul>\n<p>[MDN 文档]: <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/attachEvent\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/attachEvent</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myDiv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myDiv\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n capture<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n once<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>优点：同一个事件可以注册多个处理器，按照注册先后顺序执行，支持自定义事件。</p>\n<p>缺点：不兼容 IE6-IE8，IE9 及之后 IE 浏览器可用</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>IE 家族的<code class=\"language-text\">EventTarge.attachEvent()</code> (IE6-IE10 可用，但是 IE9 就已经可以用 addEventListener 了，直到 IE11 才不支持 attachEvent)</p>\n<p>参数：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>eventNameWithOn 以 on 作为开头的事件名称，例如”onclick”。</li>\n<li>callback 执行的回调（不接受 event 参数，可以在 window.event 对象上获取）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>缺点：不支持事件捕获，不支持自定义事件。</p>\n<p>优点：在不支持<code class=\"language-text\">addEventListener()</code>的老 IE 中可以为一个事件绑定多个处理器（执行顺序时从后到先的顺序）。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myDiv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myDiv\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">attachEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"onclick\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p>传统事件绑定、<code class=\"language-text\">EventTarget.addEventListener()</code> 和<code class=\"language-text\">EventTarge.attachEvent()</code>还有个区别在于事件处理函数中的 this 指向，<strong>前两者</strong>指向绑定事件的 DOM 元素对象，<strong>后者</strong>始终指向 window 对象。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>事件注册的兼容性写法（&#x3C;=IE8 的 IE 浏览器不支持事件冒泡，可以通过添加 polyfill 的方式兼容）：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>addEventListener<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>attachEvent<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">attachEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"onclick\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  object<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclick</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>事件取消</strong></p>\n<p>对应三种事件注册，事件取消也有三种：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>取消传统事件绑定，将对应元素上的事件属性赋值为 null。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myDiv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myDiv\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclick</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myDiv\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onclick <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>W3C 的<code class=\"language-text\">EventTarget.removeEventListener()</code>取消使用<code class=\"language-text\">EventTarget.addEventListener()</code>绑定的事件。</p>\n<p>参数：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>type</li>\n<li>listener （必须和<code class=\"language-text\">EventTarget.addEventListener()</code>指向同一个）</li>\n<li>[useCapture] 取消的事件处理是否为捕获阶段，默认为 false，true 对应捕获阶段，false 对应冒泡阶段。统一个 listener 如果分别注册在捕获阶段和冒泡阶段，则可以分别取消，互不影响。</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> myDiv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myDiv\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>IE 家族的<code class=\"language-text\">EventTarge.detachEvent()</code> (IE6-IE10，IE11 不再支持)</p>\n<p>参数：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>eventNameWithOn 以 on 作为开头的事件名称，例如”onclick”。</li>\n<li>callback 执行的回调</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myDiv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myDiv\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">attachEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"onclick\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">detachEvent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"onclick\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>阻止事件传播</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>W3C 标准</p>\n<p>使用<code class=\"language-text\">event.stopPropagation()</code>阻止事件传播（不仅仅可以阻止事件冒泡，也可以阻止其后的事件捕获）</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ow67vzejn.bkt.clouddn.com/20180830145742.png\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>还有个不常用的<code class=\"language-text\">event.stopImmediatePropagation()</code>，不仅仅能阻止事件传播（捕获和冒泡），还能阻止目标阶段执行其他注册事件（例如同时注册了多个 click 事件，则在某个事件函数中执行到<code class=\"language-text\">event.stopImmediatePropagation()</code>其后的事件函数将都不再执行）。</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>IE（IE6-IE8）</p>\n<p>使用<code class=\"language-text\">event.cancelBubble=true;</code>阻止事件冒泡。（IE6-IE8 不支持事件捕获，因此没有阻止事件捕获的方法，都不支持还阻止个毛线……）</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>阻止默认事件</strong></p>\n<p>阻止如&#x3C;a>标签点击后的默认跳转事件。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>W3C 标准</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">event.preventDefault()</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>IE (IE6-IE8)</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">event.returnValue=false;</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>传统事件绑定</p>\n<p>使用下面这两种古老写法的事件绑定的，直接在事件处理函数中<code class=\"language-text\">return false</code>:</p>\n<p>最老的写法：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">onclick</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>handleClick()<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>srcipt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\nfunction handleClick(){ // dosomthing return false; }\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>srcipt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>也很老的写法：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myDiv <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myDiv\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyDiv<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclick</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// dosomthing</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"浏览器事件机制","date":"August 30, 2018","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/canvas初探/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"canvas初探"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/SVG入门/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"SVG入门"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"9bc8460f-81de-51cd-b50e-28ef70a4a898","previousPostId":"53d7f0cf-d2c4-5283-8fca-c5ed73853023","nextPostId":"1d8898ac-e5e5-5321-9866-9044de10bc65"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}